#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:9
#, no-c-format
msgid "ldap"
msgstr "लदपः"

#. Tag: author
#: index.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Lauri.Watts; &Lauri.Watts.mail;"
msgstr "&लौरी.वाट्स; &लौरी.वाट्स.मेल;"

#. Tag: trans_comment
#: index.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid "ROLES_OF_TRANSLATORS"
msgstr "अनुवादकानां_भूमिका"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:17
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<acronym>ldap</acronym> is the lightweight directory access protocol. It "
"provides access to an X.500 directory, or to a stand-alone <acronym>LDAP</"
"acronym> server."
msgstr ""
"<acronym>ldap</acronym> इति लघुनिर्देशिकाप्रवेशप्रोटोकॉलः । एतत् X.500 निर्देशिकायाः, "
"अथवा एकान्तस्य <acronym>LDAP</acronym> सर्वरस्य प्रवेशं प्रदाति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can use the ldap KIO worker as follows:"
msgstr "भवान् ldap KIO worker इत्यस्य उपयोगं निम्नलिखितरूपेण कर्तुं शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:23
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>ldap://host:port/ou=People,o=where,c=de??sub</userinput> for a "
"subtree-query"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>ldap://host:port/ou=उपवृक्ष-प्रश्नस्य कृते जनाः,o=where,c=de??sub</"
"userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:26
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"or <userinput>ldap://host:port/cn=MM,ou=People,o=where,c=de??base</"
"userinput> for a complete branch."
msgstr ""
"अथवा <userinput>ldap://host:port/cn=MM,ou=People,o=where,c=de??base</"
"userinput> पूर्णशाखायाः कृते ।"
